              "const": "official Hub repository metadata and list_repo_files bind the immutable remote inventory; local SHA-256 binds materialized bytes; an advertised LFS SHA-256 or non-LFS Git blob SHA-1 is content-verified when available, otherwise transport and immutable-revision trust are explicit"
